
---


@startuml

' Users
class User {
  +id: String (unique)
  +name: String
  +address: String
  +birthday: Date
}

' Business Owner
class BusinessOwner {
  +linkedinAccount: String
  -User user
  *+owns: PizzaRestaurant
}

' Pizza Restaurant
class PizzaRestaurant {
  +zipCode: String
  +address: String
  +phone: String
  +website: String
  +openingHours: String
  *+offers: Pizza
  *+employs: Entertainer
}

' Pizza
class Pizza {
  +name: String
  +crustType: String
  +price: Decimal
  *+isOfferedBy: PizzaRestaurant
}

' Order
class Order {
  +id: String (unique)
  +placedAt: DateTime
  +latestDeliveryTime: DateTime
  +numberOfPeople: Integer
  *+belongsTo: HungryCustomer
  *+contains: Pizza
  *+isEntertainmentOrder: EntertainmentOrder
}

' EntertainmentOrder
class EntertainmentOrder {
  +entertainmentType: String
  +durationMinutes: Integer
  *+requires: Entertainer
}

' Entertainer
class Entertainer {
  +stageName: String
  +bio: String
  +pricePer30Minutes: Decimal
  *+worksAt: PizzaRestaurant
  *+fulfills: EntertainmentOrder
}

' Availability
class Availability {
  +dayOfWeek: String
  +startTime: Time
  +endTime: Time
  *+forEntertainer: Entertainer
  *+atRestaurant: PizzaRestaurant
}

' HungryCustomer
class HungryCustomer {
  -User user
  *+places: Order
}

' Relationships
User "1" -- "1" BusinessOwner : has
BusinessOwner "1" -- "0..*" PizzaRestaurant : owns
PizzaRestaurant "1" -- "0..*" Pizza : offers
HungryCustomer "1" -- "0..*" Order : places
Order "1" -- "0..*" Pizza : contains
Order "1" -- "0..1" EntertainmentOrder : isEntertainmentOrder
EntertainmentOrder "1" -- "1" Entertainer : requires
Entertainer "1" -- "0..*" PizzaRestaurant : worksAt
Entertainer "1" -- "0..*" Availability : has
PizzaRestaurant "1" -- "0..*" Availability : has

@enduml

---

### 📌 Notes:

- **Unique Identifiers**: All entities have a unique identifier (`id`) to ensure distinguishability.
- **Associations**:
  - A `Pizza` is unique per `PizzaRestaurant`, even if the name and price are the same.
  - An `EntertainmentOrder` is a special type of `Order`.
  - An `Entertainer` can work at multiple `PizzaRestaurants` and has availability schedules.
- **Aggregation & Composition**:
  - `Pizza` is associated with `PizzaRestaurant` (aggregation).
  - `Availability` is associated with both `Entertainer` and `PizzaRestaurant`.

